title: For the Love of Switchfoot, The Church, and C.S. Lewis
description:
Michael and Jeff talk about their shared love of Switchfoot, tighter-knit church community, and C. S. Lewis.

Michael makes his first appearance on Randos United.  He's a member of The Village Church pastored by Paul Vander Klay's dear friend Rod Hugen in Tucson, AZ and was able to meet Paul, Job, John Vandonk, and many other folks on the first leg of the ill-fated 2020 Flying Dutchmen Meetup Tour.

To join the discussion, go to https://discord.gg/aXu7Pc

The Village Church in Tucson, AZ:
http://www.villagersonline.com/

Jon Foreman's "Revenge"
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VPX7AualHNg

Switchfoot performing live on the now defunct early aughts TV show "Pepsi Smash":
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KuabRQr0HNo

Switchfoot's cover of Beyonce's "Crazy in Love"
 https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=heiswnjSVuU
